---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="L'Officina dello Shen | Shiatsu • Coppettazione • Riflessologia">
	<nav class="fixed w-full z-50 bg-[#0a0a0a]/60 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-white/5 shadow-2xl">
		<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center overflow-hidden">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
				<img src="/logo.png" alt="Logo L'Officina dello Shen" class="h-10 md:h-14 w-auto" />
			</div>
			
			<a href="https://wa.me/393489219739" class="group flex items-center gap-3 text-sm font-bold text-[#09AC90] uppercase tracking-widest shrink-0">
				WhatsApp
				<span class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#09AC90]/30 group-hover:bg-[#09AC90] group-hover:text-[#0a0a0a] transition-all duration-300 text-xs">
					→
				</span>
			</a>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<main class="overflow-x-hidden">
		<h1 class="sr-only">L'Officina dello Shen - Alessandra Ciot - Shiatsu e Benessere a Pordenone</h1>
		
		<header class="relative min-h-[85vh] md:min-h-screen bg-[#0a0a0a] text-white flex items-center pt-20 md:pt-24 overflow-hidden">
			<div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03] bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#888_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#888_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:64px_64px]"></div>
			
			<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-[1fr,auto] gap-8 md:gap-16 items-center relative z-10 py-6 md:py-10">
				<div class="max-w-4xl">
					<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[10px] md:text-sm font-medium text-[#09AC90] mb-4 md:mb-8 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] md:tracking-[0.3em]">
						L'Officina dello Shen • Percorsi individuali
					</div>
					<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-[90px] font-serif font-bold leading-[1.0] tracking-tighter mb-10 italic break-words">
						Ritrova <br/><span class="text-[#09AC90] not-italic">equilibrio</span>,<span class="text-[#09AC90] not-italic"> energia</span><br/>e <span class="text-[#09AC90] not-italic">benessere</span>.
					</h1>
					<p class="text-xl text-stone-400 max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-12 font-light italic">
						Dall'esperienza di Alessandra Ciot nasce un approccio che armonizza corpo e mente attraverso lo Shiatsu e le antiche arti del benessere.
					</p>
					<a href="https://wa.me/393489219739" class="inline-block bg-[#09AC90] text-[#0a0a0a] px-12 py-5 rounded-full font-extrabold text-lg hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-2xl">
						PRENOTA UN TRATTAMENTO
					</a>
				</div>
				
				<div class="hidden md:block relative">
					<div class="absolute -inset-10 bg-[#09AC90]/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
					<img src="/facendo_trattamento_shia.png" alt="Trattamento in corso" class="rounded-3xl w-full max-w-2xl border border-white/5 opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</header>

		<section class="py-32 bg-[#0f0f0f] border-y border-white/5">
			<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
				<div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
					<img src="/leggendo_libro_shia.png" alt="Formazione e studio" class="rounded-3xl w-full max-w-2xl border border-white/5 opacity-80 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" />
				</div>
				<div class="grid gap-12 order-1 lg:order-2">
					<div class="group">
						<h3 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic font-serif border-l-2 border-[#09AC90] pl-4">L'Officina dello Shen</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-500 font-light leading-relaxed italic">Uno spazio dedicato alla cura di sé, dove Alessandra Ciot integra tecniche millenarie per favorire il libero fluire dello "Shen" (lo spirito/energia vitale).</p>
					</div>
					<div class="group">
						<h3 class="text-white text-2xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic font-serif border-l-2 border-[#09AC90] pl-4">Approccio personalizzato</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-500 font-light leading-relaxed italic">Ogni seduta è un dialogo silenzioso con il corpo, adattato alle tue necessità specifiche attraverso l'ascolto e la presenza.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="servizi" class="py-32 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
			<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6">
				<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-20 gap-8">
					<h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-white italic">I Nostri <span class="text-[#09AC90]">Trattamenti</span></h2>
					<div class="md:w-1/3">
						<img src="/facendo_trattamento_2.png" alt="Dettaglio trattamento" class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 transition-all" />
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 max-w-[1600px] mx-auto">
					<div class="group p-8 bg-[#141414] rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-[#09AC90]/40 transition-all text-center">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic group-hover:text-[#09AC90]">Shiatsu</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-500 font-light italic leading-relaxed text-sm">Pressioni manuali profonde per stimolare il flusso energetico e sciogliere le tensioni muscolari.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="group p-8 bg-[#141414] rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-[#09AC90]/40 transition-all text-center">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic group-hover:text-[#09AC90]">Coppettazione</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-500 font-light italic leading-relaxed text-sm">Tecnica che favorisce la circolazione sanguigna e linfatica, ideale per decontrarre i tessuti e drenare le tossine.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="group p-8 bg-[#141414] rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-[#09AC90]/40 transition-all text-center">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic group-hover:text-[#09AC90]">Moxibustione</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-500 font-light italic leading-relaxed text-sm">Applicazione di calore su punti specifici per armonizzare l'energia e contrastare umidità e freddo.</p>
					</div>
					
					<div class="group p-8 bg-[#141414] rounded-3xl border border-white/5 hover:border-[#09AC90]/40 transition-all text-center">
						<h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic group-hover:text-[#09AC90]">Riflessologia</h3>
						<p class="text-stone-500 font-light italic leading-relaxed text-sm">Riequilibrio dell'intero organismo attraverso il massaggio stimolante delle zone riflessogene dei piedi.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-24 bg-[#0f0f0f]">
			<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6">
				<div class="text-center mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-[#09AC90] text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif italic mb-4">Sedi dei trattamenti</h2>
				</div>

				<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
					<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=ASD+Bamboo+Piazza+Garibaldi+26+Tiezzo+Azzano+Decimo" 
					target="_blank" 
					class="block p-6 md:p-12 border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] rounded-[2rem] hover:border-[#09AC90]/50 hover:bg-[#141414] transition-all group">
						<h4 class="text-white text-3xl font-serif mb-4 font-bold italic group-hover:text-[#09AC90] transition-colors">ASD Bamboo</h4>
						<p class="text-white opacity-80 leading-relaxed">
							Piazza Garibaldi, 26 <br/> 
							Tiezzo di Azzano Decimo (PN)
						</p>
						<div class="mt-6 text-[#09AC90] text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2">
							Apri in Maps <span class="group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">→</span>
						</div>
					</a>
					
					<a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Dream+Fitness+Wellness+Via+Nogaredo+78+Cordenons" 
					target="_blank" 
					class="block p-6 md:p-12 border border-white/5 bg-[#0a0a0a] rounded-[2rem] hover:border-[#09AC90]/50 hover:bg-[#141414] transition-all group">
						<h4 class="text-white text-3xl font-serif mb-4 font-bold italic group-hover:text-[#09AC90] transition-colors">Dream Fitness Wellness</h4>
						<p class="text-white opacity-80 leading-relaxed">
							Via Nogaredo, 78 <br/> 
							Cordenons (PN)
						</p>
						<div class="mt-6 text-[#09AC90] text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest flex items-center gap-2">
							Apri in Maps <span class="group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">→</span>
						</div>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer class="py-20 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-t border-white/5 text-stone-600">
			<div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-10">
				<div class="text-center md:text-left">
					<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
						<img src="/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="h-8 w-auto grayscale opacity-50" />
						<span class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-white tracking-tighter uppercase italic">L'Officina dello Shen</span>
					</div>
					<p class="text-sm italic mb-2">di Alessandra Ciot</p>
					<a class="text-white hover:text-[#09AC90]" href="tel:+393489219739">+39 348 921 9739</a>	
				</div>
				<div class="text-center md:text-right text-xs uppercase tracking-widest opacity-40 font-mono italic">
					© 2026 L'Officina dello Shen • Pordenone e provincia
				</div>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</main>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
	html, body {
		overflow-x: hidden;
		width: 100%;
		position: relative;
		background-color: #0a0a0a;
	}
</style>